title: FPort optimization
body:
Dear editors,

Please find my contributions to version -03 branch of the SCHC-over-LoRaWAN draft.
I implemented the ideas I developed after IETF105 in Montreal, about FPort optimization. I took the opportunity to clean-up the draft and move myself into the authors list.
Fell free to pick or reject the commits you want.

I did not implement the RCS idea to move to AES-CMAC, after discussion with @Oliv4945. We can discuss that topic in another branch if you want.

Let me know what you think.
Julien
